KoF Mailbox: An Early Look At The Nike Air Jordan 4 White Cement 2016 Retro (Video) * KicksOnFire.com

"Nike Air" is not bulletproof, as it turns out. Just because you slap on the original branding on a shoe and call it a remaster doesn't mean people are going to buy them in bunches, as evidenced by the Air Jordan 6 Maroon.

item.description:
adidas Yeezy Boost 350 Pirate Black (2016 Restock List) * KicksOnFire.com

Release Date: February 19, 2016 Price: $200 The Pirate Black colorway of the adidas Yeezy Boost 350 is set to restock on February 19, 2016. We first saw this Pirate Black colorway make its debut in August of 2015 and is now set to return six months later.
